query:
DELETE p1 FROM providers p1
INNER JOIN providers p2 
WHERE p1.id > p2.id 
AND p1.name = p2.name 
AND p1.stateCode = p2.stateCode 
AND COALESCE(p1.city, '') = COALESCE(p2.city, '');
